{"tid":2506220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"受梘液影響導致大量泡沫　觀塘5000萬海濱音樂噴泉暫停開放","createTime":"2021-04-27T07:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T07:15:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb94333bf939417c35e7350e5522f99a7d2dfe01","tid":2506220,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587762-20210426.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587762-20210426.htm&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=220e961a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587762-20210426.htm&h=32d26349\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587762-20210426.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n康文署宣布，關閉觀塘海濱音樂噴泉及暫停噴泉表演，直至另行通告。<br />\n<br />\n康文署表示，由於音樂噴泉及互動嬉水區的池水，懷疑受梘液影響而導致大量泡沫出現，現已關閉以排走池水及徹底清潔。"}]}